Bhn Home Security Services, LLC Overview
  Bhn Home Security Services, LLC filed as a Foreign Limited Liability in the State of Florida on Thursday, July 3, 2008 and is approximately nine years old, as recorded in documents filed with Florida Department of State. A corporate filing is called a foreign filing when an existing corporate entity files in a state other than the state they originally filed in. This does not necessarily mean that they are from outside the United States.   




