Where all your home controls come together
No more wandering the house flipping switches and punching keypads before bed. Vivint SkyControl Panel is a smart home hub that bundles all your smart home controls in one place, giving you control of lights, locks, garage doors, thermostats, and security systems from one spot.






A panic button to call for immediate help
If you notice someone prowling your property, SkyControl lets you watch through your security cameras from a safe location. For situations that turn dangerous, SkyControl comes with a  panic button to sound the alarm and open instant communication with security monitoring teams.






A panic button to call for immediate help
If you notice someone prowling your property, SkyControl lets you watch through your security cameras from a safe location. For situations that turn dangerous, SkyControl comes with a  panic button to sound the alarm and open instant communication with security monitoring teams.









Easy and intuitive navigation
Centralizing home controls onto one dashboard creates seamless smart home experiences that you might not notice until you remember them later. With its high-definition touch-screen, SkyControl gives you easy access to your smart home, convenient notifications, and a place to review all your home security video.










Encrypted network



Backup battery



Wireless signal



Secure signal. Secure home. 
It takes a secure wireless network to create complete home security. Vivint SkyControl encrypts smart home signals to secure both video and smart home devices. And the bright, HD display shows you a glowing signal of your home’s status from across the room.


Stay protected when the power goes out
Sometimes a storm might knock out power. Other times, it's a motivated burglar with insulated wire cutters. In either case, SkyControl's backup battery keeps your smart home controls, your security system, and your notifications working long enough to keep your home safe.


Leave the wires for the birds
The centerpiece of Vivint Smart Home systems, SkyControl moderates all wireless communications between you and and the Vivint Smart Home cloud. Wireless functionality gives you better protection. And a dedicated cellular connection means more reliable communication and no solid lines for burglars to cut.







